ommodores football team|Vanderbilt]] || <!--NOTE-->\n|-\n! 5 || 161\n| [[Tyler_Johnson_(American_football)|Tyler Johnson]] || [[Wide Receiver|WR]] || 2019 Minnesota Golden Gophers football team|Minnesota || <!--NOTE-->\n|-\n! 6 || 194\n| <!--PLAYER--> || <!--POSITION--> || <!--COLLEGE--> || <!--NOTE-->\n|-\n!  rowspan=\"2\" | 7 || 241\n| <!--PLAYER--> || <!--POSITION--> || <!--COLLEGE--> || from [[2020 New England Patriots season|New England]]\n|-\n! 245\n| <!--PLAYER--> || <!--POSITION--> || <!--COLLEGE--> || from San Francisco\n|}\n'''Draft trades'''\n*The Buccaneers traded their 2020 first-round and 2020 fourth-round selections to the [[2020 San Francisco 49ers season|San Francisco 49ers]] in exchange for San Francisco's 2020 first-round and 2020 seventh-round selections.<ref>{{cite web|last=Goodbread|first=Chase|title=Bucs trade with 49ers to draft OL Tristan Wirfs|work=NFL|url=http://www.nfl.com/news/story/0ap3000001110874/article/bucs-trade-with-49ers-to-draft-ol-tristan-wirfs|publisher=National Football League|date=April 23, 2020|accessdate=April 23, 2020}}</ref>\n*The Buccaneers traded their 2020 seventh-round selection and wide receiver [[DeSean Jackson]] to the [[2019 Philadelphia Eagles season|Philadelphia Eagles]] in exchange for Philadelphia's sixth-round [[2019 NFL Draft|2019]] selection.<ref>{{cite web|last=Williams|first=Charean A.|title=Bucs trade DeSean Jackson to Eagles|work=Pro Football Talk|url=https://profootballtalk.nbcsports.com/2019/03/11/bucs-trade-desean-jackson-to-eagles/|publisher=NBC Sports|date=March 14, 2019|accessdate=March 14, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Staff==\n{{Tampa Bay Buccaneers staff}}\n\n==Current roster==\n{{Tampa Bay Buccaneers roster}}\n\n==Preseason==\nThe Buccaneers' preseason opponents and schedule will be announced in the spring.\n\n==Regular season==\n<!--===Schedule===-->\n\n===2020 opponents===\nListed below are the Buccaneers' opponents for [[2020 NFL season|2020]]. Exact dates and times will be announced in the spring.<re